---
title: Community
---

.main-content
  .container
    %h1
      %i.fa.fa-comments
      Community
      %small and contacts

    %p
      There are several ways by which you can engage with the mpv community
      of users and developers. Here's the complete list:

    %table.table.table-condensed
      %tr
        %td(colspan="3")
          %h3
            %i.fa.fa-terminal
            Internet Relay Chat

          %p
            This is the preferred way to discuss mpv use and development. Never ask to
            ask - just state your question. Stick around until someone replies.


      %tr
        %td Users channel
        %td(colspan="2")
          = link_to '#mpv on irc.libera.chat', 'ircs://irc.libera.chat:6697/mpv'

      %tr
        %td
          Development channel
          %small (no fun allowed)
        %td(colspan="2")
          = link_to '#mpv-devel on irc.libera.chat', 'ircs://irc.libera.chat:6697/mpv-devel'

      %tr
        %td(colspan="3")
          %h3
            %i.fa.fa-bug
            GitHub issue tracker

          %p
            This is the preferred way to report bugs.

      %tr
        %td Issue tracker
        %td(colspan="2")
          = link_to 'https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv/issues', 'https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv/issues'

      %tr
        %td(colspan="3")
          %h3
            GitHub wiki pages

          %p
            Publicly editable wiki hosted on github.

      %tr
        %td Wiki
        %td(colspan="2")
          = link_to 'https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv/wiki', 'https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv/wiki'

      %tr
        %td FAQ
        %td(colspan="2")
          = link_to 'https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv/wiki/FAQ', 'https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv/wiki/FAQ'

      %tr
        %td User scripts (third-party)
        %td(colspan="2")
          = link_to 'https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv/wiki/User-Scripts', 'https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv/wiki/User-Scripts'

      %tr
        %td Front ends etc. (third-party)
        %td(colspan="2")
          = link_to 'https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv/wiki/Applications-using-mpv', 'https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv/wiki/Applications-using-mpv'
